title: FBI v. White House: Different tales on Porter background
text:
FBI v. White House: Different tales on Porter background Tuesday, February 13, 2018 - 02:06 
FBI Director Christopher Wray contradicted the White House version of events surrounding the background check for Rob Porter — a former top aide accused of domestic abuse by two ex-wives. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
